<SYNC Start=6047100><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6048637><P Class=KRCC>
안녕하시오
<SYNC Start=6050702><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6052107><P Class=KRCC>
